longBusinessSummary: Aranjin Resources Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties in Mongolia. The company explores for copper deposits. Its flagship asset is the Bayan Undur project located in Bayankhongor province, Mongolia. The company was formerly known as Five Star Diamonds Limited and changed its name to Aranjin Resources Ltd. in June 2020. Aranjin Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia.
